Which of the following measures are taken to ensure the confidentiality of your health information in this study?
A) All participant data will be made publicly accessible; 
B) Participant data will be stored without any identifiers on an unsecured server; 
C) Participant data will be assigned a unique identifier and stored on a secured encrypted server with limited access; 
